# Apple Mac / IOS

I don't use any Apple devices other than an Apple TV and an iPad for ForeFlight. 
So while I can't personally recommend anything, I've heard good things about these.

- [NetNewsWire](https://netnewswire.com/): Incredibly polished, fast, and open source. You can also sync via iCloud.
- [Reeder](https://reederapp.com/): Pretty flexible, and makes processing a lot of feeds easy.

{% break djot list %}

# Linux

I don't run any Linux computers with a GUI, but these seem like decent choices.

- [Mozilla Thunderbird](https://www.thunderbird.net/): I use this as an email client too and it does the job.
- [Raven Reader](https://ravenreader.app/): Great UI, open source, and available on Windows too.
- [Newsboat](https://github.com/newsboat/newsboat): RSS/Atom in the terminal

